{"type": "article", "id": 21975, "title": "harto 家具", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-05T08:00:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021105512FrpwKdA6DJbkZVt.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">法国家具品牌 harto 推出的家具参加了巴黎家居装饰博览会和科隆家具展。这组家具都以浅色的木材为主体，点缀以有趣的彩色，年轻而活泼。除了颜色外，家具的形状也使用了活泼的元素。餐具柜门上采用了倾斜的纹路，有点像船帆，挂壁式隔板设计成上小下大的梯形，比普通的柜子则增加了一份轻巧灵活。点击这里可以查看更多信息。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110549M0m8HgARrTtEJifN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.45721271\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110550TZPU0qCGBK3fMrpz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110550RYDbZ6uFnckUoHw0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65403423\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110550gPJ9VhMTfRiZ0D41.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110551SOKcyFjzaf3IB25X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><br></div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}